{"title": "Red Badge of Courage (Version 3)", "description": "A youth, caught up in patriotic fervor and dreams of glory, enlists in the Union Army. In his first battle, though, he runs away. <br>Deeply ashamed of his cowardice, and imagining the snickers and gibes of comrades behind his back, he rejoins his unit and in later fights puts himself in the vanguard, where his battle frenzy awes his companions. He is seeking a battle wound \u2013 his own red badge of courage. (Summary by Mark Smith)", "duration": 19034, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "523", "name": "Stephen Crane"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/redbadge_2304_librivox/redbadgecourage_2304.jpg", "copyright_year": "1895", "genres": ["Action & Adventure Fiction", "Historical Fiction", "War & Military Fiction"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "Mark F. Smith"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Mark F. Smith"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Laurie Anne Walden"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "KevinS"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "Chapter 1", "readers": [204], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/redbadge_2304_librivox/redbadgeofcourage_01_crane_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1551}, {"section": 2, "title": "Chapter 2", "readers": [204], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/redbadge_2304_librivox/redbadgeofcourage_02_crane_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1161}, {"section": 3, "title": "Chapter 3", "readers": [204], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/redbadge_2304_librivox/redbadgeofcourage_03_crane_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1217}, {"section": 4, "title": "Chapter 4", "readers": [204], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/redbadge_2304_librivox/redbadgeofcourage_04_crane_64kb.mp3", "duration": 477}, {"section": 5, "title": "Chapter 5", "readers": [204], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/redbadge_2304_librivox/redbadgeofcourage_05_crane_64kb.mp3", "duration": 917}, {"section": 6, "title": "Chapter 6", "readers": [204], "path": "https://www.